ick-the-two-teams%2Farticleshow%2F117888948.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Meta%20CTO%20said%202025%20will%20likely%20prove%20the%20metaverse%20to%20be%20a%20visionary%20bet%20or%20'legendary%20misadventure%2C'%20leaked%20memo%20shows%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222872%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Andrew%20Bosworth%20Meta%20Connect%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f451d90d59cc64f5b02ded%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221526%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAndrew%20Bosworth%2C%20the%20CTO%20of%20Meta%2C%20told%20staff%20in%20a%20memo%20that%202025%20is%20%26quot%3Bmost%20critical%26quot%3B%20for%20its%20metaverse%20bets.%20%3Cp%3EMeta%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMeta's%20CTO%20said%202025%20is%20crucial%20for%20Metaverse's%20success%20or%20failure%20in%20a%20leaked%20memo%20seen%20by%20BI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAndrew%20Bosworth%20said%20Meta%20needs%20to%20%26quot%3Bdrive%20sales%2C%20retention%2C%20and%20engagement%26quot%3B%20for%20mixed%20reality.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20added%20Reality%20Labs%20plans%20to%20launch%20%26quot%3Bhalf%20a%20dozen%26quot%3B%20more%20AI-powered%20wearable%20products.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMeta's%20chief%20technology%20officer%20thinks%202025%20could%20be%20a%20make-or-break%20year%20for%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffacebook-metaverse%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emetaverse%3C%2Fa%3E%20bets%2C%20Business%20Insider%20has%20learned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAndrew%20%26quot%3BBoz%26quot%3B%20Bosworth%20told%20staff%20this%20year%20is%20%26quot%3Bmost%20critical%26quot%3B%20to%20prove%20the%20metaverse%20is%20either%20a%20visionary%20feat%20or%20a%20%26quot%3Blegendary%20misadventure%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20an%20internal%20memo%20from%20November%2C%20viewed%20by%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20titled%20%26quot%3B2025%3A%20The%20Year%20of%20Greatness%2C%26quot%3B%20shared%20on%20Meta's%20internal%20forum%20Workplace%2C%20Bosworth%20said%20its%20Reality%20Labs%20division%20plans%20to%20launch%20half%20a%20dozen%20more%20AI-powered%20wearable%20devices%20%E2%80%94%20but%20did%20not%20specify%20a%20timeline%20or%20provide%20further%20details.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20drive%20sales%2C%20retention%2C%20and%20engagement%20across%20the%20board%20but%20especially%20in%20MR%20%5Bmixed%20reality%5D%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20Horizon%20Worlds%20on%20mobile%20absolutely%20has%20to%20break%20out%20for%20our%20long-term%20plans%20to%20have%20a%20chance.%20If%20you%20don't%20feel%20the%20weight%20of%20history%20on%20you%2C%20then%20you%20aren't%20paying%20attention.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20year%20likely%20determines%20whether%20this%20entire%20effort%20will%20go%20down%20as%20the%20work%20of%20visionaries%20or%20a%20legendary%20misadventure.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBosworth%20also%20referred%20to%20Steven%20Levy's%20book%2C%20%26quot%3BInsanely%20Great%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20details%20how%20the%20Macintosh%20computer%20was%20created%20by%20small%20teams%20of%20one%20to%20three%20people.%20Later%20in%20the%20memo%2C%20Bosworth%20added%20that%20he%20has%20seen%20smaller%20teams%20%26quot%3Bachieve%20better%20results%20than%20our%20more%20generously%20funded%20teams.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20the%20Meta%20CTO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-reality-labs-beats-nearly-all-sales-user-targets-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%20a%20series%20of%20reorgs%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20its%20Reality%20Labs%20division%2C%20which%20is%20responsible%20for%20its%20augmented%20and%20virtual%20reality%20products.%20As%20part%20of%20the%20changes%2C%20the%20unit%20that%20Reality%20Labs%20COO%20Dan%20Reed%20previously%20led%20will%20now%20be%20run%20by%20Meta%20COO%20Javier%20Olivan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20also%20reshuffled%20the%20reporting%20lines%20of%20other%20Reality%20Labs%20executives%2C%20who%20now%20report%20to%20other%20key%20figures%20in%20Meta's%20core%20business%2C%20signaling%20the%20division%20has%20become%20a%20bigger%20priority%20for%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20Meta's%20Reality%20Labs%20unit%20reported%20a%20record%20%241.08%20billion%20in%20revenue%20in%20its%20fourth-quarter%20earnings.%20However%2C%20the%20mixed%20reality-focused%20division%20also%20recorded%20its%20biggest-ever%20quarterly%20operating%20loss%20of%20%244.97%20billion.%20The%20division%20has%20racked%20up%20losses%20of%20about%20%2460%20billion%20since%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20didn't%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20BI%2C%20made%20outside%20normal%20working%20hours.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeta%20CEO%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20spoke%20about%20the%20company's%20smart%20glasses%20in%20an%20all-hands%20meeting%20last%20week%2C%20in%20which%20he%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-meta-employees-intense-year-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20employees%20to%20%26quot%3Bbuckle%20up%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20an%20%26quot%3Bintense%20year.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20company%20sold%20more%20than%20a%20million%20units%20of%20its%20AI-powered%20smart%20glasses%20in%202024%2C%20which%20Zuckerberg%20said%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bgreat%20start%26quot%3B%20but%20that%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20going%20to%20move%20the%20needle%20and%20the%20business%20in%20a%20core%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20added%20that%20Meta's%20trajectory%20this%20year%20will%20give%20it%20a%20good%20indication%20of%20whether%20smart%20glasses%20will%20become%20a%20%26quot%3Blong-term%20grind%26quot%3B%20and%20whether%2C%20in%20the%20near%20term%2C%20AI%20glasses%20will%20become%20a%20%26quot%3Breally%20prominent%20computing%20platform.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ERead%20the%20full%20memo%20Bosworth%20sent%20to%20employees%3A%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3E2025%3A%20The%20Year%20of%20Greatness%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3ENext%20year%20is%20going%20to%20be%20the%20most%20critical%20year%20in%20my%208%20years%20at%20Reality%20Labs.%20We%20have%20the%20best%20portfolio%20of%20products%20we've%20ever%20had%20in%20market%20and%20are%20pushing%20our%20advantage%20by%20launching%20half%20a%20dozen%20more%20AI%20powered%20wearables.%20We%20need%20to%20drive%20sales%2C%20retention%2C%20and%20engagement%20across%20the%20board%20but%20especially%20in%20MR.%20And%20Horizon%20Worlds%20on%20mobile%20absolutely%20has%20to%20break%20out%20for%20our%20long%20term%20plans%20to%20have%20a%20chance.%20If%20you%20don't%20feel%20the%20weight%20of%20history%20on%20you%20then%20you%20aren't%20paying%20attention.%20This%20year%20likely%20determines%20whether%20this%20entire%20effort%20will%20go%20down%20as%20the%20work%20of%20visionaries%20or%20a%20legendary%20misadventure.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EI've%20been%20re-reading%20%26quot%3BInsanely%20Great%2C%26quot%3B%20Steven%20Levy's%20history%20of%20the%20Macintosh%20computer.%20If%20you%20haven't%20read%20it%20the%20book%20chronicles%20the%20incredible%20efforts%20of%20individuals%20working%20in%20teams%20of%201-3%20to%20build%20a%20device%20that%20more%20than%20any%20other%20marked%20the%20consumer%20era%20of%20personal%20computing.%20What%20I%20find%20most%20fascinating%20about%20it%20is%20the%20way%20that%20even%20people%20who%20left%20the%20program%20on%20bad%20terms%20(it%20was%20not%20particularly%20well%20managed)%20speak%20about%20the%20work%20they%20did%20there%20with%20an%20immense%20sense%20of%20pride.%20There%20was%20a%20widespread%20cultural%20expectation%2C%20set%20by%20none%20other%20than%20a%20young%20Steve%20Jobs%2C%20that%20the%20work%20needed%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Binsanely%20great.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EOn%20paper%202024%20was%20our%20most%20successful%20year%20to%20date%20but%20we%20aren't%20sitting%20around%20celebrating%20because%20know%20it%20isn't%20enough.%20We%20haven't%20actually%20made%20a%20dent%20in%20the%20world%20yet.%20The%20prize%20for%20good%20work%20is%20the%20opportunity%20to%20do%20great%20work.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cstrong%3EGreatness%20is%20our%20opportunity.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20live%20in%20an%20incredible%20time%20of%20technological%20achievement%20and%20have%20placed%20ourselves%20at%20the%20center%20of%20it%20with%20our%20investments.%3Cem%3E%20There%20is%20a%20very%20good%20chance%20most%20of%20us%20will%20never%20get%20a%20chance%20like%20this%20again.%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cstrong%3EGreatness%20is%20a%20choice.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Many%20people%20have%20ben%20at%20the%20precipice%20of%20opportunity%20and%20failed%20to%20achieve.%20For%20the%20most%20part%20they%20failed%20to%20even%20challenge%20themselves.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20should%20be%20doing%20the%20best%20work%20of%20your%20career%20right%20now.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20You%20should%20be%20pushing%20yourself%20to%20grow%20where%20needed%20and%20doubling%20down%20on%20your%20strengths.%20When%20you%20look%20back%20on%20this%20time%20I%20want%20you%20to%20feel%20like%20you%20did%20everything%20in%20your%20power%20to%20make%20the%20most%20of%20it.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20don't%20need%20big%20teams%20to%20do%20great%20work.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIn%20fact%2C%20it%20may%20make%20it%20harder.%20One%20trend%20I've%20observed%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years%20is%20that%20our%20smaller%20teams%20often%20go%20faster%20and%20achieve%20better%20results%20than%20our%20more%20generously%20funded%20teams.%20Not%20only%20that%2C%20they%20are%20much%20happier!%20In%20small%20teams%20there%20is%20no%20risk%20of%20falling%20into%20bad%20habits%20like%20design%20by%20committee.%20You%20should%20be%20so%20focused%20on%20results%20that%20being%20in%20a%20bunch%20of%20docs%20or%20meetings%20is%20too%20frustrating%20to%20bear.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20path%20is%20clear.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EYou%20don't%20need%20to%20come%20up%20with%20a%20bunch%20of%20new%20ideas%20to%20do%20this%20great%20work.%20Most%20people%20in%20the%20organization%20just%20need%20to%20execute%20on%20the%20work%20laid%20out%20before%20them%20to%20succeed.%20It%20is%20about%20operational%20excellence.%20It%20is%20about%20master%20craftsmanship.%20It%20is%20about%20filling%20our%20products%20with%20%26quot%3BGive%20A%20Damn%26quot%3B.%20%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20about%20having%20pride%20in%20our%20work.%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EI%20will%20close%20with%20an%20Arnold%20Glasow%20quote%3A%20%26quot%3BSuccess%20isn't%20a%20result%20of%20spontaneous%20combustion.%20You%20must%20set%20yourself%20on%20fire.%26quot%3B%202025%20is%20the%20year.%20Let's%20be%20on%20fire.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20a%20Meta%20employee%3F%20Got%20insight%20to%20share%3F%20Contact%20the%20reporter%20Jyoti%20Mann%20via%20Signal%20at%20jyotimann.11%20or%20email%20at%20jmann%40businessinsider.com.%20Reach%20out%20from%20a%20nonwork%20device.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-cto-metaverse-reality-labs-legendary-misadventure-memo-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738587135000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a0b6d17bb3f854015b7a60%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-cto-metaverse-reality-labs-legendary-misadventure-memo-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20leaked%20memo%20obtained%20by%20BI%2C%20Meta's%20CTO%20called%202025%20%26quot%3Bthe%20year%20of%20greatness%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20it%20is%20the%20%26quot%3Bmost%20critical%26quot%3B%20year%20for%20its%20metaverse%20bets.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%2