20exchange%20between%20the%20treasury%20benches%20and%20the%20Opposition%20after%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20claimed%20that%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20was%20sent%20to%20the%20inauguration%20of%20Donald%20Trump%20as%20US%20President%20to%20ensure%20a%20US%20invite%20for%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%C2%A0The%20Prime%20Minister%20seated%20in%20the%20House%2C%20BJP%20MPs%20led%20by%20Parliamentary%20Affairs%20Minister%20Kiren%20Rijiju%20strongly%20objected%20to%20Mr%20Gandhi's%20remark%20and%20said%20he%20cannot%20make%20such%20unsubstantiated%20statements%20linked%20to%20the%20country's%20foreign%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20House%20during%20the%20debate%20on%20the%20Motion%20of%20Thanks%20to%20the%20President's%20Address%2C%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20said%20he%20%26quot%3Bstruggled%26quot%3B%20to%20maintain%20his%20attention%20through%20the%20President's%20address%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20I%20had%20heard%20pretty%20much%20the%20same%20President's%20address%20the%20last%20time%20and%20the%20time%20before%20that%20and%20the%20time%20before%20that%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20the%20same%20laundry%20list%20of%20things%20that%20the%20government%20has%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gandhi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20said%20the%20country%20has%20not%20failed%20to%20tackle%20the%20problem%20of%20unemployment.%20%26quot%3BNeither%20the%20UPA%20government%20nor%20today's%20NDA%20government%20has%20given%20a%20clear-cut%20answer%20to%20the%20youth%20of%20India%20about%20employment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%20said%20the%20share%20of%20manufacturing%20in%20India's%20GDP%20had%20fallen%20from%2015.3%20per%20cent%20in%202014%20to%2012.6%20per%20cent%20today%20despite%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government's%20Make%20in%20India%20push.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20blaming%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%20It%20would%20not%20be%20fair%20to%20say%20he%20did%20not%20try.%20Make%20in%20India%20was%20a%20good%20idea%20but%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20failed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%20said%20the%20country's%20record%20in%20organising%20production%20is%20dismal.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20handed%20over%20organisation%20of%20production%20to%20the%20Chinese.%20Every%20time%20we%20use%20a%20phone%2C%20wear%20a%20Chinese%20shirt%20or%20sneakers%2C%20we%20pay%20a%20tax%20to%20China.%20If%20we%20don't%20focus%20on%20production%20and%20continue%20to%20focus%20only%20on%20consumption%2C%20we%20will%20run%20huge%20deficits%2C%20increase%20inequality%20and%20run%20into%20a%20social%20problem%20because%20of%20unemployment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%20said%20China%20controls%20the%20bulk%20of%20production%20data%20and%20US%20the%20consumption%20data.%20%26quot%3BSo%20if%20India%20wants%20to%20talk%20about%20AI%2C%20it%20has%20to%20answer%20the%20question%2C%20what%20data%20is%20going%20to%20power%20that%3F%20The%20answer%20today%20is%20India%20does%20not%20have%20the%20data%2C%20neither%20production%20data%20nor%20consumption%20data%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20pushing%20for%20the%20need%20to%20build%20a%20production%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20connection%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20referred%20to%20the%20Trump%20inauguration%20event.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20talk%20to%20the%20United%20States%2C%20we%20would%20not%20send%20the%20foreign%20minister%20three-four%20times%20to%20get%20an%20invite%20for%20our%20Prime%20Minister%20because%20if%20we%20had%20a%20production%20system%20and%20we%20were%20working%20on%20these%20technologies%2C%20the%20US%20president%20would%20come%20here%20and%20invite%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remark%20drew%20loud%20protests%20from%20the%20treasury%20benches.%20Mr%20Rijiju%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20cannot%20make%20such%20serious%2C%20unsubstantiated%20statements.%20This%20is%20about%20the%20relationship%20between%20two%20countries.%20He%20is%20making%20unverified%20statements%20about%20the%20invitation%20of%20our%20Prime%20Minister.%20He%20should%20be%20responsible.%20If%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20has%20the%20information%2C%20he%20must%20tell%20the%20House%20who%20has%20told%20him%20that%20the%20Foreign%20Minister%20visited%20for%20this%20purpose.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%20responded%20with%20a%20quip.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20sorry%20if%20that%20question%20disturbed%20you.%20I%20apologise%20for%20disturbing%20your%20peace%20of%20mind.%20I%20am%20sorry.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rijiju%20said%20Mr%20Gandhi%20must%20apologise%20for%20lying%20in%20the%20House.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20must%20be%20serious%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20Mr%20Gandhi's%20speech%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20Dr%20Jaishankar%20trashed%20his%20claim%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%20The%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20said%20Mr%20Gandhi's%20%26quot%3Blies%20may%20be%20intended%26quot%3B%20to%20serve%20a%20political%20purpose%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20they%20damage%20the%20nation%20abroad%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ELeader%20of%20Opposition%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20deliberately%20spoke%20a%20falsehood%20about%20my%20visit%20to%20the%20US%20in%20December%202024.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnI%20went%20to%20meet%20the%20Secretary%20of%20State%20and%20NSA%20of%20the%20Biden%20Administration.%20Also%20to%20chair%20a%20gathering%20of%20our%20Consuls%20General.%20During%20my%20stay%2C%20the%20incoming%20NSA-designate%20met%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Dr.%20S.%20Jaishankar%20(%40DrSJaishankar)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDrSJaishankar%2Fstatus%2F1886368544226504960%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%203%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLeader%20o