articleshow%2F117884481.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20was%20laid%20off%20from%20my%206-figure%20consulting%20job.%20Instead%20of%20looking%20for%20another%20job%20in%20the%20industry%2C%20I%20became%20a%20sex%20educator.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22788%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22headshot%20of%20a%20man%20outside%20in%20a%20blue%20shirt%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F679d1dee7bb3f854015b5d58%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22591%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPaul%20Travis.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Paul%20Travis%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPaul%20Travis%20started%20his%20career%20as%20a%20marketing%20consultant%20but%20left%20the%20industry%20after%20a%20layoff.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20launched%20a%20dating%20program%20for%20singles%20over%2040%20during%20the%20pandemic%20called%20The%20School%20for%20Love.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENow%2C%20Travis%20is%20a%20certified%20sex%20educator%20and%20embraces%20a%20digital%20nomad%20lifestyle.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Paul%20Travis%2C%20the%2059-year-old%20founder%20of%20The%20School%20for%20Love%20based%20in%20Bainbridge%20Island%2C%20Washington.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%20sex%20educator%20and%20the%20founder%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.schoolforlove.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20School%20for%20Love%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20have%20a%20BA%20in%20mathematics%20and%20computer%20science%20and%20completed%20the%20Harvard%20Executive%20Program%20in%20Brand%20Management.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20two-year%20stint%20as%20the%20VP%20of%20marketing%20for%20Net%20Nanny%20Software%20in%20the%20early%202000s%2C%20I%20took%20my%20Harvard%20postgrad%20executive%20branding%20work%20into%20consulting%20for%20a%20variety%20of%20client%20engagements%2C%20from%20rebranding%20to%20new%20product%20launch%20to%20marketing%20systems%20implementation%2C%20in%20industries%20from%20food%20manufacturing%20to%20laser%20lighting%20to%20SaaS%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20December%202013%2C%20I%20was%20engaged%20to%20implement%20a%20customer%20community%20program%20for%20Avalara%2C%20a%20fintech%20company.%20Eighteen%20months%20later%2C%20I%20transitioned%20to%20full-time%20employment%20as%20a%20senior%20program%20manager%20for%20the%20web%20marketing%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20losing%20this%20job%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20leave%20consulting%20behind%20and%20become%20a%20sex%20educator.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ca18e7eb-8624-4fb4-90e1-78301ba967da%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20was%20laid%20off%20in%20September%202020%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAvalara%20brought%20its%20first%20CMO%20aboard%20in%20late%202019.%20In%20January%202020%2C%20my%20manager%20told%20me%20that%20the%20two%20program%20management%20roles%20inside%20marketing%20would%20be%20eliminated.%20I%20set%20out%20to%20find%20another%20position%20within%20the%20company%2C%20but%20with%20the%20onset%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20and%20financial%20uncertainty%2C%20most%20hiring%20came%20to%20a%20standstill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20entered%20spring%2C%20I%20mentally%20braced%20for%20losing%20more%20than%20%2410%2C000%20monthly%20in%20income%20and%20benefits.%20I%20was%20earning%20six%20figures%20a%20year%20when%20I%20left%20Avalara.%20I'd%20enjoyed%20growing%20with%20the%20company%20through%20an%20IPO%2C%20but%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20I%20was%20tired%20of%20the%20increasing%20energy%20drain%20and%20uninterested%20in%20another%20corporate%20gig.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20excited%20and%20uncertain%20when%20I%20was%20laid%20off%20in%20September%202020%2C%20but%20I%20trusted%20that%20I%20was%20embarking%20on%20the%20next%20big%20chapter%20of%20my%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22986997eb-8619-4f55-91bb-f974f12b4379%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20knew%20I%20was%20interested%20in%20midlife%20dating%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20David%20Bowie%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAging%20is%20an%20extraordinary%20process%20whereby%20you%20become%20the%20person%20you%20always%20should've%20been.%26quot%3B%20I%20learned%20how%20important%20variety%20is%20to%20me%2C%20so%20returning%20to%20a%20past%20chapter%20like%20consulting%20(like%20returning%20to%20a%20past%20lover)%20didn't%20call%20to%20me%20%E2%80%94%20I%20wanted%20to%20build%20a%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20researched%20a%20few%20ideas%20that%20had%20been%20in%20the%20back%20of%20my%20mind%20and%20decided%20to%20focus%20on%20midlife%20dating%2C%20with%20which%20I%20was%20extremely%20comfortable%20after%20my%20divorce%20following%20a%2019-year%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20lockdowns%20and%20masking%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20I%20understood%20how%20difficult%20this%20was%20for%20singles%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewresearch.org%2Fshort-reads%2F2020%2F08%2F20%2Fkey-takeaways-on-americans-views-of-and-experiences-with-dating-and-relationships%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emany%20of%20whom%20say%20it%20was%20already%20more%20challenging%20than%20during%20the%20last%2010%20years%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20my%20years%20of%20study%20in%20nonviolent%20communication%2C%20tantra%2C%20and%20interpersonal%20work%2C%20I%20felt%20a%20passion%20brewing%20to%20help%20people%20in%20this%20very%20different%20realm%20of%20training%2C%20propelled%20by%20COVID-19.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e6a2328d-0cbc-4d15-86f4-68ed9ad51b90%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20started%20an%20online%20program%20for%20singles%20over%2040%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%202021%2C%20I%20launched%20my%20twelve-week%20online%20program%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Great%20Dating%20Reset%2C%26quot%3B%20for%20%24999%20under%20the%20umbrella%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FPandemic.Love%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPandemic.Love%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20help%20spiritual%20singles%20over%2040%20cultivate%20%26quot%3Bauthintimacy%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20a%20portmanteau%20of%20authenticity%20and%20intimacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20found%20my%20initial%20clients%20from%20advertising%20on%20Facebook.%20It%20was%20heartwarming%20to%20help%20Sue%2C%20a%2052-year-old%20woman%2C%20navigate%20a%20new%20relationship%20and%20save%20her%20from%20being%20taken%20advantage%20of%20for%20a%20few%20thousand%20dollars.%20Equally%20so%20for%20Sally%2C%20who%20had%20been%20painfully%20dumped%20from%20a%20seven-year%20relationship%20and%20found%20esteem%20and%20self-love%20through%20the%20homework%20exercises.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20rebranding%20in%20January%202022%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FSchoolForLove.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESchoolForLove.com%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I've%20run%20two%20to%20three%20group%20programs%20online%20each%20year.%20Later%20in%202022%2C%20I%20created%20and%20hosted%20a%20summit%20for%20this%20same%20audience%2C%20%26quot%3BDare%20to%20Date%20Differently%2C%26quot%3B%20along%20with%2012%20other%20speakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2238c86d3c-01b2-445f-91b1-f57e66e64593%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20next%20became%20a%20certified%20sex%20educator%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20speaking%20regularly%20with%20people%20about%20their%20dating%20lives%20and%20our%20program%2C%20I%20found%20just%20how%20often%20singles%20brought%20up%20sexuality%20as%20a%20core%20area%20of%20worry%2C%20shame%2C%20or%20frustration.%20I%20set%20out%20in%202023%20to%20study%20with%20Dr.%20Martha%20Tara%20Lee%20in%20Singapore%20and%20became%20a%20certified%20sex%20educator%2C%20certified%20by%20AASECT%20(the%20American%20Association%20of%20Sex%20Educators%2C%20Counselors%2C%20and%20Therapists).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20haven't%20yet%20reached%20my%20former%20salaried%20income%20level%2C%20but%20I've%20lowered%20my%20expenses%20by%20renting%20out%20my%20house%20and%20having%20a%20tight%20budget.%20I%20downsized%20into%20my%20Sprinter%20van%20and%20embraced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvan-life-road-trip-convinced-nomadic-lifestyle-is-for-me-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evan%20life%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I'm%20thankful%20technology%20allows%20me%20to%20work%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fremote-worker-promoted-senior-manager-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edigital%20nomad%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I've%20traveled%20more%20in%20the%20past%20three%20years%20than%20ever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b1235de6-c574-4f7d-ab61-0b003734d060%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI'd%20make%20the%20choice%20all%20over%20again%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20delighted%20to%20make%20a%20genuine%20difference%20in%20people's%20love%20lives%20rather%20than%20in%20corporate%20software%20and%20marketing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20writing%20a%20book%20on%20%26quot%3BAuthintimacy%2C%26quot%3B%20so%20I%20spend%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20on%20social%20media%20and%20marketing%20systems%2C%20talking%20to%20clients%20and%20prospects%2C%20and%20managing%20several%20freelancers.%20I'm%20in%20the%20process%20of%20launching%20my%20second%20program%2C%20Authintimacy%20Brotherhood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20work%20six%20to%20seven%20days%20a%20week%20from%20anywhere%20between%208%20a.m.%20and%208%20p.m.%2C%20but%20I%20take%20time%20every%20day%20to%20be%20in%20nature%2C%20play%20with%20my%20dog%2C%20and%20nurture%20my%20spirit%20away%20from%20the%20computer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESociety%20teaches%20us%20to%20get%20on%20the%20%26quot%3Blife%20escalator%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20everything%20will%20eventually%20work%20out%20for%20retirement.%20That's%20not%20how%20my%20life%20has%20worked%2C%20but%20I%20have%20no%20fears%20about%20retirement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20had%20some%20devastating%20detours%2C%20awesome%20advances%2C%20and%20circuitous%20change-ups.%20I%20have%20no%20career%20regrets%20and%20appreciate