22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kerala%20Woman's%20Death%20Reveals%20Chilling%20Tale%20Of%20Humiliation%2C%20Toxic%20Torture%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20husband%20of%20a%2025-year-old%20woman%2C%20who%20was%20found%20dead%20at%20her%20home%20in%20Kerala's%20Malappuram%20last%20week%2C%20has%20been%20arrested%20after%20the%20woman's%20family%20alleged%20that%20he%20tortured%20her%20physically%20and%20mentally.%20Police%20have%20registered%20a%20case%20under%20charges%20of%20abetment%20to%20suicide%20and%20cruelty%20against%20women%20by%20their%20husbands%20or%20their%20relatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victim%2C%20Vishnuja%2C%20married%20Prabhin%20in%20May%202023.%20It%20was%20an%20arranged%20marriage.%20A%20male%20nurse%2C%20Prabhin%20allegedly%20humiliated%20Vishnuja%20regularly.%20He%20would%20tell%20her%20she%20was%20not%20beautiful%20and%20insult%20her%20for%20not%20getting%20a%20job%2C%20her%20family%20has%20alleged.%20They%20also%20accused%20him%20of%20beating%20her%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BDidn't%20Know%20He%20Beat%20My%20Child%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVishnuja's%20father%20Vasudevan%20told%20the%20media%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20used%20to%20tell%20her%20she%20looked%20too%20thin.%20He%20would%20not%20let%20her%20ride%20on%20his%20bike%2C%20claiming%20she%20was%20unattractive.%20Right%20after%20the%20wedding%2C%20he%20told%20her%20to%20get%20a%20job%20and%20that%20she%20could%20not%20expect%20to%20live%20off%20his%20salary.%20She%20took%20a%20few%20exams%2C%20but%20she%20could%20not%20get%20a%20job.%20She%20tried%20very%20hard%2C%20but%20she%20couldn't%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20The%20heartbroken%20father%20said%20Vishnuja%20did%20not%20tell%20them%20about%20the%20harassment%20and%20they%20have%20only%20found%20out%20about%20it%20from%20her%20friends%20after%20her%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20faced%20problems%2C%20she%20supported%20us.%20But%20she%20never%20allowed%20us%20to%20intervene%20in%20her%20marital%20issues.%20She%20refused%20to%20reveal%20any%20details%20about%20what%20she%20was%20going%20through.%20When%20we%20wanted%20to%20help%20her%2C%20she%20insisted%20she%20would%20change%20him.%20I%20have%20only%20come%20to%20know%20now%20that%20he%20beat%20my%20child.%20We%20are%20hearing%20he%20had%20affairs%20with%20other%20women%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20Vasudevan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20alleged%20that%20he%20suspects%20Vishnuja%20was%20murdered.%20%26quot%3BI%20believe%20he%20(Prabhin)%20killed%20and%20hanged%20her.%26quot%3B%20The%20woman's%20family%20has%20also%20alleged%20that%20Prabhin's%20family%20backed%20his%20harassment%20of%20their%20daughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BHer%20WhatsApp%20Connected%20To%20His%20Phone%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20aftermath%20of%20Vishnuja's%20tragic%20death%2C%20her%20friends%20have%20come%20forward%20with%20chilling%20accounts%20of%20what%20she%20was%20going%20through.%20According%20to%20a%20report%20in%20Manorama%20online%2C%20a%20friend%20of%20hers%20has%20said%20Prabhin%20tortured%20Vishnuja%20physically%20and%20mentally.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20she%20couldn't%20take%20it%20anymore%2C%20she%20started%20sharing%20everything%20with%20me.%20I%20told%20her%20to%20return%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20friend%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVishnuja's%20friend%20accused%20Prabhin%20of%20tracking%20her%20chats%20to%20see%20if%20she%20shared%20her%20ordeal%20with%20her%20friends%20or%20family.%20%26quot%3BHer%20WhatsApp%20number%20was%20linked%20to%20his%20phone.%20She%20never%20spoke%20to%20us%20freely%20on%20WhatsApp.%20We%20would%20talk%20on%20Telegram%20so%20that%20he%20did%20not%20know.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ctable%3E%3Cthead%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Cth%20colspan%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3EHelplines%3C%2Fth%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3C%2Fthead%3E%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3EVandrevala%20Foundation%20for%20Mental%20Health