he%20help%20of%20a%20couple%20of%20women%20workers.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGrowing%20up%2C%20I%20observed%20a%20lack%20of%20support%20among%20our%20extended%20family%20members.%20Whereas%2C%20I%20would%20see%20how%20my%20mother%20insisted%20we%20share%20meals%20after%20we%20came%20home%20from%20school.%20I%20cherished%20these%20values%2C%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20with%20her%20in%20these%20difficult%20times%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Kinshuk%2C%20it%20was%20challenging%20to%20build%20a%20customer%20base%20for%20the%20products.%20He%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20going%20to%20the%20colony%20gate%20and%20coming%20back%20again%20and%20again.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20to%20convince%20people%20to%20buy%20our%20products.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20that%E2%80%99s%20when%20he%20says%20his%20father%20motivated%20him.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20he%20could%20not%20speak%20for%20a%20while%20post-surgery%2C%20he%20wrote%20on%20a%20paper%20and%20asked%20me%20to%20quit%20hesitating.%20He%20gave%20an%20example%20of%20how%20he%20himself%20would%20personally%20invite%20passengers%20on%20his%20bus%20despite%20being%20the%20owner.%20This%20motivated%20me%20to%20go%20door-to-door%20with%20our%20food%20samples.%20This%20simple%20strategy%20helped%20us%20get%20orders%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fplugins%2Fpost.php%3Fhref%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.facebook.com%252Ftriptifoodsmrt%252Fposts%252Fpfbid07mSnWbtQiTjQMGu6a5iq7Zjj5Z78NaNooKvK71XYyttWRznuYTwMgsoGBkGqUSPDl%26show_text%3Dtrue%26width%3D500%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22498%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20small%20venture%2C%20begun%20with%20a%20rested%20resolve%2C%20now%20sees%20its%20presence%20beyond%20Meerut%20in%20places%20like%20Moradabad%2C%20Ghaziabad%2C%20Aligarh%2C%20and%20Noida.%20Laveena%E2%80%99s%20products%20are%20available%20both%20offline%20and%20online%2C%20including%20on%20platforms%20like%20Amazon.%20%E2%80%9COn%20average%2C%20we%20get%20300%20orders%20a%20month.%20The%20profits%20from%20the%20business%20have%20helped%20us%20clear%20loans%20of%20Rs%2015%20lakh%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Kinshuk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20been%2013%20years%20since%20the%20inception%20of%20their%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F366432%2Fhomemade-food-pickles-jams-in-kerala-homemaker-runs-business-organic-garden-bees-of-beena%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efood%20business%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Laveena%20today%20embodies%20an%20inspiring%20narrative%20of%20overcoming%20adversity.%20%E2%80%9CI%20do%20not%20think%20of%20myself%20as%20a%20beacon%20of%20hope%20and%20inspiration%20but%20through%20my%20example%2C%20I%20want%20to%20show%20that%20one%20should%20not%20be%20bogged%20down%20in%20any%20circumstance%20and%20lose%20courage%2C%20come%20what%20may%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20each%20jar%20of%20pickles%2C%20bottle%20of%20squash%2C%20and%20pack%20of%20jam%20that%20leaves%20her%20home%20carries%20a%20piece%20of%20her%20story%20%E2%80%94%20a%20story%20of%20resilience%20and%20perseverance%2C%20forged%20in%20adversity%20and%20nurtured%20by%20the%20reassuring%20warmth%20of%20her%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3B%20%3Cem%3EAll%20images%20courtesy%20Kinshuk%20Jain%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738553400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Flaveena-food-business-2-1736142125.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D395455%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Laveena%20Jain%2C%20a%2056-year-old%20cancer%20survivor%2C%20turned%20her%20years%20of%20culinary%20passion%20into%20a%20thriving%20business%2C%20known%20today%20as%20%E2%80%98Laveena%E2%80%99s%20Tri